institutions around the country

00:01:45.230 --> 00:01:48.790
and more specifically, in this
area -- to the Kennedy Center,

00:01:48.790 --> 00:01:52.220
the Washington Memorial -- I'm
sorry, the Washington Monument,

00:01:52.220 --> 00:01:55.740
the National Zoo -- and if you
read the news just this past Monday

00:01:55.740 --> 00:02:00.750
