a love of reading in his kids.

00:29:25.520 --> 00:29:27.580
United Through Reading
was the first non-profit

00:29:27.580 --> 00:29:29.630 position:56%
to promote the read aloud experience

00:29:29.630 --> 00:29:31.840
to bring separated
families together.

