00:51:16.060 --> 00:51:17.360
Ninety-five percent.

00:51:17.360 --> 00:51:18.660
I'll take that.

00:51:18.660 --> 00:51:19.960
I'll take that.

00:51:19.960 --> 00:51:23.230
