01:07:04.350 --> 01:07:07.000
in being helpful in the that.

01:07:07.000 --> 01:07:09.470
I'm not sure that I
have the temperament

01:07:09.470 --> 01:07:13.130
for working on the inside.

01:07:13.130 --> 01:07:19.800
But I'm a terrific heckler and
I'd be very happy in that role.

01:07:19.800 --> 01:07:21.100
&gt;&gt; David Rubenstein:
So what book do you --

01:07:21.100 --> 01:07:22.400
how many books do you read a year?

