01:07:49.210 --> 01:07:50.510
Yeah.

01:07:50.510 --> 01:07:53.800
&gt;&gt; David Rubenstein: And today,
if you look back on your career --

01:07:53.800 --> 01:07:56.780
do you have any regrets in
leaving the practice of law?

